# a simple naive saw synth to use in test patches

@ in note
@ in decay
@ in trig

@ out out

+ miditofreq mtf
> _in_@note mtf@in

+ sawosc saw
> mtf@out saw@freq

+ segment env
= 1 env@val1
= 0 env@val2
> _in_@decay env@dur
> _in_@trig env@clock

+ mult vca
> saw@out vca@in1
> env@out vca@in2

> vca@out _out_@out

